%A5t-ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-M5U91kUR-TYsdZojkictCQ">Lãm Liễu Hồn “Đinh Châu thái bạch tần” chi thập, nhân thành nhất chương - 覽柳渾汀洲採白蘋之什，因成一章</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Di/author-ORfogRLuJo5mkrUrEUhFVA">Từ Di</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Gia-C%C3%A1t/Phi%E1%BA%BFm-%C4%90%E1%BB%99ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-h%E1%BB%93/poem-LYd_F3WBkzE9xwPy2o20XA">Phiếm Động Đình hồ - 泛洞庭湖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Gia-C%C3%A1t/author-OgCmFbzsG1Vv369sQ2n63w">Nguyễn Gia Cát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/Thanh/poem-YzY6mvhzoMt_zftmuprI-w">Thanh - 聲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/author-kzRUGlov9gv6H-eBsn_tAA">Thôi Đồ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Thu-khu%C3%AA/poem-yrH1cUWPKDoek8FCl93etg">Thu khuê - 秋閨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C4%83n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%A5t-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-thi%E1%BA%BFt-kho%C3%A1i-h%C3%AD-t%E1%BA%B7ng-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ca/poem-loqXR_RH7MuCHDDme5Ig1w">Văn Hương Khương thất thiếu phủ thiết khoái hí tặng trường ca - 閿鄉姜七少府設膾，戲贈長</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
